-- ft.page: Row
    
-- ft.markdown: 

A row is a container component that stacks a list of children horizontally.

`Note`: Make sure to close your row container using the `end`
syntax. This is mandatory.

`-- end: <container-name>`

-- ft.h3: Usage

-- ft.code:
lang: ftd

\-- ftd.row:

\;; << Child components >>

\-- end: ftd.row

-- ft.h3: Attributes

Row accepts the [container attributes](container/) as well all the [common attributes ](common/).
